!results/parametric/demo_02/baseline/
# Re-ignore any SQLite that lands inside the baseline dir (the db lives one level up anyway).
results/parametric/demo_02/baseline/*.db
results/parametric/demo_02/baseline/*.db-wal
results/parametric/demo_02/baseline/*.db-shm

